<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head lang="en">
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>테스트 (<%=pid%>) <%=testset%></title>
  <link href="http://cdn.bootcss.com/bootstrap/3.2.0/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
  <link href="/stylesheets/sqy.css" rel="stylesheet"/>
</head>
<body class="has-navbar-fixed-top">
<nav class="navbar navbar-default navbar-fixed-top">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="navbar-header col-sm-2">
      <a class="navbar-brand" href="/">THEMIS</a>
    </div>
    <div id="navbar" class="navbar-collapse collapse">
      <ul class="nav navbar-nav navbar-nav-switch col-sm-8">
        <li class="col-sm-12"><a id="btnSwitch" status="0" class="text-center" href="#">풀이 시작</a></li>
      </ul>
      <ul class="nav navbar-nav navbar-nav-next col-sm-2 disabled">
        <li class="col-sm-12"><a id="btnNext" class="text-center" href="/next/<%=pid%>/<%=step%>">다음 단계 (<%=step+1%>/3)</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div><!--/.nav-collapse -->
  </div>
</nav>
<input id="duration" type="hidden" name="duration" value="<%=duration%>"/>
<input id="timeset" type="hidden" name="timeset" value="<%=timeset%>"/>
<div class="container">
  <div class="alert alert-info">
    <h4>주의사항：</h4>
    <p></p>
    <p>[문제 1]을 푸는 동안에는 [문제 2]을 보거나 풀 수 없습니다. &nbsp;&nbsp;[문제 1]의 제한 시간 <%=duration / 60 / 2%>분이 지나면 자동적으로 [문제 2]로 넘어갑니다.</p>
    <p>각 문제에서 입력한 내용은 자동적으로 저장됩니다.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="test">
    <div class="question question1">
      <div class="backup" id="acBak1">
        <input class="btn btn-success" id="acBtn1" type="button" value="문제1"/>
      </div>
      <div class="alarm alert alert-warning" id="alarmClock1"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-time"></span> <%=duration / 60 / 2%>:00</div>
      <%- partial('stimulus' + testset[(step-1)*2 + 0] + '.html') %>
      <form id="form1" class="form-horizontal form-percent">
        <p>본 사건 1에 대하여</p>
        <p>다음의 확률을 총 합이 100이 되도록 기입하시기 바랍니다.</p>
        <br/>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label class="form-label col-sm-2 text-right">피고인은 유죄이다</label>
          <div class="col-sm-3">
            <input type="number" name="guilty" value="0"/>
            <label class="percent">%</label>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label class="form-label col-sm-2 text-right">피고인은 유죄가 아니다</label>
          <div class="col-sm-3">
            <input type="number" name="not_guilty" value="0"/>
            <label class="percent">%</label>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label class="form-label col-sm-2 text-right">총</label>
          <div class="col-sm-3">
            <input type="number" name="total" value="0" readonly/>
            <label class="percent">%</label>
          </div>
        </div>
        <input type="hidden" name="step" value="<%=step%>"/>
        <input type="hidden" name="question" value="1"/>
        <input type="hidden" name="stimulus" value="<%=testset[(step-1)*2+0]%>"/>
        <input type="hidden" name="pid" value="<%=pid%>"/>
        <input type="hidden" name="type" value="<%=type%>"/>
      </form>
    </div>
    <div class="question question2">
      <div class="backup pending" id="acBak2">
        <input class="btn btn-success hide" id="acBtn2" type="button" value="문제2"/>
      </div>
      <div class="alarm alert alert-warning" id="alarmClock2"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-time"></span> <%=duration / 60 / 2%>:00</div>
      <%- partial('stimulus' + testset[(step-1)*2 + 1] + '.html') %>
      <form id="form2" class="form-horizontal form-percent">
        <p>본 사건 2에 대하여</p>
        <p>다음의 확률을 총 합이 100이 되도록 기입하시기 바랍니다.</p>
        <br/>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label class="form-label col-sm-2 text-right">피고인은 유죄이다</label>
          <div>
            <input type="number" size="5" name="guilty"/>
            <label class="percent">%</label>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label class="form-label col-sm-2 text-right">피고인은 유죄가 아니다</label>
          <div>
            <input type="number" size="5" name="not_guilty"/>
            <label class="percent">%</label>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label class="form-label col-sm-2 text-right">총</label>
          <div>
            <input type="number" size="5" name="total"/>
            <label class="percent">%</label>
          </div>
        </div>
        <input type="hidden" name="step" value="<%=step%>"/>
        <input type="hidden" name="question" value="2"/>
        <input type="hidden" name="stimulus" value="<%=testset[(step-1)*2+1]%>"/>
        <input type="hidden" name="pid" value="<%=pid%>"/>
        <input type="hidden" name="type" value="<%=type%>"/>
      </form>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<script type="text/javascript" src="//code.jquery.com/jquery-1.11.2.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.2/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="/javascripts/test1.js"></script>
</body>
</html>